    About this hotel

    This unfussy beachfront hotel is 5 km from the Fondation Lorin arts center and 6 km from Cape Malabata, which has a lighthouse and a castle. …

    Featuring colorful touches and wall art, the laid-back rooms have TVs and air-conditioning, as well as balconies offering seating and bay views.

    An airy, informal restaurant overlooks the bay. Other amenities include a bar, an outdoor pool and a terrace.
